      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/bitcoin-jumps-most-in-more-than-a-month-amid-fed-rate-cut-optimism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币回吐了之前上涨势头，此前市场预期美联储将降低借贷成本，从而增加对投机性资产的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/bitcoin-jumps-most-in-more-than-a-month-amid-fed-rate-cut-optimism</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 16:05:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
